criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age between 18 and 70 years;

          -  Healthy volunteers;

          -  Individuals to participate in the study who referred to becoming superior of the
             subsequent intact students (Molars or premolars, either side);

          -  Individuals of both sexes.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Gastroesophageal complaints;

          -  Limitation of mouth opening;

          -  Pathologies of airways;

          -  Individuals invited to the study who reported bilateral upper posterior tooth loss;

          -  Inability to respond to the questionnaire
